data.description:
This one has it all !

Four bedroom 2 1/2 bath colonial single
family on a private drive. A true must see
with hardwood floors throughout and new
berber carpet in the family room. Come see
the all Trex deck as you enjoy the largest lot
in Independence. Large master bedroom
with deluxe master bath with Jacuzi tub.
Upgraded lighting package throughout. This
is the perfect home for someone looking to
start a family. Great schools a growing area.
The pictures speak for themselves! Close to
RT 234, I 66 and RT 28. Basement already
studed and ready for drywall. Rough in for
gas fireplace already done. Hurry while its
still available!

Neighborhood Description

Great neighborhood full of wonderful people!
data.whatILove: Largest lot in Independence! Private drive! Located by shopping and quick access to I-66 and Route 234.
